## Features:
- Mock trading with paper trading
- Track multiple stocks simultaneously
- Beautiful Jetpack Compose UI
- Real-time data synchronization
- Offline support with local caching
- No personal data collection

## Requirements:
- Android 8.0 (API 26) or higher
- Internet connection for trading data

## Known Limitations:
- Paper trading only (no real brokerage integration)
- Mock data for demonstration purposes
- Limited to Indian stock symbols
